# template service (skeleton)

Module: `github.com/dobriygolang/project-nordly/services/template`. **Copy to create new services** — see `AGENTS.md`.

## Layers

```
cmd/template/app/run.go          → DI
internal/app/api/template/       → gRPC/HTTP (one RPC per file)
internal/example/model|repository|service/
```

HTTP `:8099`, gRPC `:9199`. Do not deploy as production.
